            <a href="http://www.musictoday.com/#about-us-2"><h1>About Us</h1></a>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-content">
           <p>We&#8217;re Musictoday, industry leaders in direct-to-fan ecommerce. With more than 15 years under our belts in creating sales and marketing solutions for brands, artists, labels, festivals and merchandisers.</p>
<p>Our 150 person team in Crozet, Virginia, uses our very own ecommerce, ticketing and fan club platforms. We&#8217;re a one-stop-shop with client services, marketing, IT, customer service, and fulfillment all under one roof. We&#8217;ve worked with over 500 artists, athletes and brands, from Bruce Lee to the Rolling Stones. Drop us a line and see what we can do for you.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
